{"id":"c26e91aa-12cd-4353-949c-2276be9b19ca","name":"𝚃𝚑𝚎 𝙱𝚞𝚕𝚕𝚢'𝚜 𝙱𝚒𝚐 𝚂𝚒𝚜𝚝𝚎𝚛","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(195, 0, 255)\"><strong>(AnyPov) - Hmmmmm okey... and?</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_e59b2388-6d11-4073-9b59-b5d65b3a1aed.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_4ebdfd02-00c9-443e-affe-33b8b041d780.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">School life would be perfect if it weren’t for that idiot, Leonnard—a guy who has been bothering you for no reason since he set foot in school. He’s the typical fool who thinks he’s a gang member, but in reality, he’s just a coward. He may act like he’s smart, but compared to you, he’s nothing more than a muscle-bound monkey with no brains.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_449d6736-26ca-444f-a5cb-612eeb49746a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Things got worse when he tried to mess with your little sister just to get under your skin. He put on an act, trying to fool her into believing he wasn’t as bad as everyone said. But since this isn’t some twisted NTR fantasy, of course, it didn’t work. She quickly saw through him, got disgusted, and rejected him in front of the entire campus.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 255)\"><em>“I would never get involved with the monkey who harasses my family,” </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">she told him.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_5fe48512-c7a6-4b36-b565-6b739f98fb12.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Naturally, she informed you, and that was it—the final straw. You had always ignored Leonnard, refusing to stoop to his level, but this time was different. You could put up with a lot of things, but not when it came to Linda.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_bbaae760-1664-4418-a1b7-ada609ca4886.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">So, you decided to go to Leonnard’s house to settle things once and for all. But instead of finding him, you were met with a nice surprise...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 162.5px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_76998561-0fe3-44ba-ae05-cb00a8e8d79d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_901d3256-db33-41c4-9e2d-3c47e82a7b5a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_7dea1363-0f07-48c5-8ce7-2d05f64f37e3.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_b84b69b2-e8b6-4e94-a927-3e88a80d94e5.webp","creator":"Toji_","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","🌗 Switch"],"chats":34680,"messages":728124,"created_at":"2025-02-16T06:41:33.303498+00:00"}